&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;An opportunity has arisen to join our kind, friendly and dedicated team in Breast Screening. We are looking for someone who excels in customer/patient service, has strong communication skills and team spirit. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a fixed 6 month post &lt;span&gt;covering&lt;/span&gt; reception when required, answering the telephone and assisting our patients. We are very busy on the phone so an excellent telephone manner is essential, this will predominantly be the main task.&lt;/p&gt;
